PrecisAmendments to the ONTARIO FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1989 which establish (a) a quota and a close time on angling for lake herring in Lake Simcoe, (b) length limits on various species caught in a number of small lakes, (c) Division 33 and revise the boundaries of Divisions 19 and 27, respectively, (d) new fish sanctuaries in known spawning grounds, and (e) make minor corrections to the fines (items 53 and 53.1) in Schedule XIII.
